<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>1-620.05</num>
  <heading>Employee rights.</heading>
  <text>Employees shall be protected against penalty or reprisal for reporting an unsafe or unhealthful working condition or practice, or assisting in the investigation of such condition or practice.</text>
